cleaningModal.title: Enhanced Clean
cleaningModal.description:
Samuel committed to Airbnb’s 5-step enhanced cleaning process—a set of standards developed in partnership with experts, for the times of COVID-19 and beyond.

Here’s what Samuel committed to doing before every stay:

items.title: Sanitize surfaces
items.subtitle: Sanitize every high-touch surface, down to the doorknob

items.title: Use approved products
items.subtitle: Use cleaners approved by health experts, like disinfectants with 70% alcohol or higher

items.title: Thoroughly clean
items.subtitle: Refer to our extensive checklists while cleaning room-by-room

items.title: Wear a mask and gloves
items.subtitle: Help avoid cross-contamination by wearing a mask and gloves

items.title: Wash all linens
items.subtitle: Wash linens at a high temperature setting

items.title: Follow all other local guidance
items.subtitle: Comply with local laws, including any additional safety or cleaning guidelines

htmlDescription.htmlText:
Enjoy a beautiful condo located at the heart of Downtown Toronto with close proximity to everything. Amazing views of Lake Ontario, High speed WiFi, Netflix, Washing machine/dryer and basic amenities will all be available.

Steps away from:
-CN Tower
-Rogers Centre
-Ripleys Aquarium
-Air Canada Centre
-Union Station
-Entertainment District
-PATH underground Walkway

Other things to note
Please treat the house with the same respect you would do yours. Please be respectful and mindful of the neighbours. No noise policy needs to be followed during the duration of your stay.

Please note that there’s no access to all of the amenities due to COVID-19

NO SMOKING ALLOWED IN THE UNIT. A FINE OF $500 WILL BE CHARGED TO YOU IF YOU SMOKE IN THE UNIT.
